Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:09.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kagami Yoshimizu Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3rd year, class B...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The ambiguous 3cm? Does that \Nmean it's plushy? Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wrapping is a uniform, \Nargh, it's not an act, pooh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta do your best, gotta just do it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's time to catch 'n' release, eek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Between sweat (whoop) Sweat (whoop){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darlin', darlin', freeze! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kinda lethargic, something's kinda comin' out{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you... Oh wait, one \Nof those was different{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worrywarts, high metal bars {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tasty thoughts... And that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The heated body of that flying you-know-who{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's what you call a normal girlie{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Am I the only one surprised? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.62,0:00:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seconds on pork-bone broth \Nramen with wire-hard noodles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.77,0:00:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Da da da da da {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pom-poms cheer squad{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.66,0:00:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's get cherry pie {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happy fun welcoming party {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look up! Sensation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah! Feeling of existence, \Ndot dot small planet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.41,0:00:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Collided and it melted away, in total awe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go all out to sing, shi-ranger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take it away! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should be the one who'll \Nbe laughing in the end{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I have the sailor suit \N← This is my conclusion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's only Monday! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already in a bad mood? What to do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really prefer the summer outfits \N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until we approach 3 pixels, \Nno hesitations please ★{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do your best, be energetic {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My darlin', darlin' please! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How were the exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just like usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tattered and torn, like I've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the exam period, you \Nhave more free time than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before you know it, time \Nalways happens to pass by,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you end up cramming \Nthe night before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you need to keep this \Nyear's entrance exams in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Base of the Sun"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the suspect's room, authorities seized
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,several thousand items of \Nvarious manga and games...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This broadcast again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was another person like \Nyou in the news again, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I hear it, I \Nthink it's really unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They always lash out at manga \Nand stuff so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many good \Nmanga titles out there too,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they never focus on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true... I kinda feel bad about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you really are \Na good person after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when I complain like that, a \Nnormal person would just mock me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and say "Otaku are so desperate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at the people around \Nme, when there are two sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one absorbs something from the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, like Yu-{\i1}chan {\i0}and Sis \NYui, or Kagami and Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's what Sis and I \Nwere talking about this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather attached \Nto Miyuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, Minami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys get along so well, \Nyou look like you're sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Absorbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-{\i1}chan{\i0}, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd have forgotten if Tsukasa \Nhadn't mentioned it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you happy to have people celebrate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but when you get to our age,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you don't feel happy about \Ngetting a year older anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm really happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get a driver's \Nlicense or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, now I can play \Nmature games and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been playing them openly already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got a year older, but you \Nhaven't changed a bit, inside or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, don't people think you're \Nolder than you actually are?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-{\i1}chan{\i0} looks so mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. When I step out in my normal clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sometimes mistaken for an office lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You skip over college altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your case, when you \Ngo out in street clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you go back to grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say, from \Nthis day forth, I am an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first place, if \Nyou've become a good adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you wouldn't be so \Nhot-headed over games and manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to have a childish \Nheart full of dreams and passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So exactly which side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While Sis is at her job,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to secretly prepare \Nfor her birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's get on \Nwith the preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Happy Birthday, Sis"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Happy Birthday"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good timing. It's Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll be back soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I forgot to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at work is celebrating my birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't need dinner tonight, \Nbecause I'll be coming home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka, this is tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yui-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you can take that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hopes after graduating, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have dreams and stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's really hard when \Nyou actually think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to college, \Nwhat you will do afterward
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may depend on the department you major in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First pick: Nutrition...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second pick: Clothing design... \NThird pick: Marketing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I like to cook and sew and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You wrote your \Ndreams out, huh, Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so all three choices are pre-med, \Nthough I chose different colleges.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Miyuki-{\i1}san{\i0}. \NYour objectives are so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you, Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My first choice is pre-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,second choice is economics, and \Nthird choice is literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not all that interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to be interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"First pick: Brigade leader"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Second pick: Master of the Divine Fist of the South Star" \N"Third pick: Anime storyboard artist"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, they're out there. The type \Nthat tries to get a laugh like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, don't you have a special \Ntalent other than staring at games?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special talents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can recite the names \Nof every single Pok_mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing in its own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,though it has nothing to \Ndo with your future plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always pick from the bottom \Nwhen you buy magazines and manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like people have \Npicked up the copies up top.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you want one that's \Nas clean as possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I understand how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like going to one of \Nthose revolving sushi restaurants,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and putting your orders in instead \Nof picking up the ready-made plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the fish on the orders on \Nthe belt tends to get dried up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami, you really do that?! \NYou're such a horrible customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! You don't do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always think about how you \Nread such wordy books, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a light novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like manga, feeling-wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is it the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got illustrations all over the \Nbook, and they use simple expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try reading one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that one has been turned into an anime,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll catch up on that front...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're talking about a \Nmanga, you check both out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying how the original \Nwork has its own goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.11,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to try reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I must decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kagami, you read a lot of books \Nin general, not just light novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you stock up on knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you feel like it enriches \Nyour heart, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's nutrition for my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going along those lines, \Nyou stock up on sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you become physically enriched as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magazines like the one you're reading now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they have text serials \Ntoo, and not just comics?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always stare at the \Nillustrations they put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So despite everything you're always saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your love really doesn't add up to much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read past all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, all right, I'll read it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, don't bother. You \Ndon't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just so many other things \Nto read that I passed over them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm telling you it's all \Nright! I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my world history textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left it on my desk at home after \Ngoing over what we learned in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata, lend me your world history textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.16,0:09:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You leave your books at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Impossible! [laugh]" "Haruka!" \N"I won't give Haruka to you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hiiragi, you have quite \Na fun-looking textbook there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um, this is, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not making much progress...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I guess I'll go \Nfind something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought some of what I bought \Nthe other day would still be left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's a good way \Nto get my mind off things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, they're closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:52.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"We have finished business for the day."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.70,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a challenge set against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be 320 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, when you're all irritated,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you make a lot of little mistakes, and \Nyou end up even more irritated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.04,0:10:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that happens. Nothing \Nyou do goes right, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you'd call it a negative spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I baked a \Ncake. Would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying for entrance exams is tough,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we have to change gears every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'll bake cookies tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that'll be stress relief! \NI'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Later..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I end up stressed on this front now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.82,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, Iwasaki-{\i1}san{\i0}? That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are always so busy, they \Nkeep passing by each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Sis has her entrance exams,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I shouldn't get in the way of her studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'll be talking a bit more softly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-{\i1}chan{\i0}, when you're off the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's play a game head-to-head! A match!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last year I'll \Nbe wearing this outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about it that way, \Nyou get really emotional about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite handkerchief \Nthat I thought I'd lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in the pocket of my summer uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we have some octopus 'n' wasabi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oyoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything about it has \Nchanged, so I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure rains a lot... After \Nall, it's the rainy season.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when you think it's too \Nhot, it suddenly gets cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem because we \Njust switched uniforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. You guys are still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you're lucky that you \Ncan change outfits freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much easier to wear uniforms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you don't have to think \Nabout what to wear each morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, you know... You're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rainy season! It's all soppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much rain, it gets you depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a topic that will \Nbrighten the conversation up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first wedding anniversary \Nis coming up, right, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Time flies by.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skies of the rainy \Nseason pose a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is the heart of Miss \NYui, whose husband is abroad,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.29,0:12:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though their wedding \Nanniversary is fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I was wrong to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'm used to \Nhaving this much emotional pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Drink something warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it still depresses me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! At this rate, someday my \Nlove is going to rust as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you went to a car \Nrepair shop or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you'd get all better \Nin forty-five minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't kill you to comfort me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That didn't take forty-five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, you still haven't gotten \Nthat outfit back from Matsuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't tell her to \Nhurry up and give it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll make it her own before you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a problem. I really like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-{\i1}san {\i0}and Tsukasa-{\i1}san \N{\i0}have two older sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you a little jealous, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I'm totally jealous \Nof how both of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata and Miyuki, are only children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if the cast is that big, \Nyou can do all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the story of a mother \Nand her four daughters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.12,0:14:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who eagerly wait for the \Nreturn of their father,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who left for the battlefield \Nin the old days in America,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or a female bandit ring that \Nonly targets objects of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, there's one too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, when it comes to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.66,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything turns into an anime or a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kagami, did you go shopping \Nfor dinner ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa, did you forget to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you forgot? Mom and \NDad aren't here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Was their vacation starting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. So we were supposed to go \Nshopping for dinner ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I called your cell and left a \Nvoicemail on it too, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"1 new message"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri, we can just make do \Nwith what's in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I was totally set on making something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you can do it another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, it's all you guys' \Nfault, Kagami, Tsukasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll go right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that was because of \Nyour attitude, Matsuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, does she even \Nknow what she needs to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's up with her? She doesn't \Nlike to cook that much anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she all worked up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, you don't have the \Nshopping list on you, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so worried, why \Ndidn't you go yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Matsuri was \Nreally worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual store didn't have any saffron,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I said that we could probably \Nuse curry powder instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sis said that since we came \Nout, we might as well look,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to the supermarket \Nthat's further away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you didn't have to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, let's make dinner. \NI'm starving already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Sorry to make you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all we have left is \NMatsuri's special dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It looks really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's got just the right \Ngolden-brown baked color, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Matsuri-{\i1}oneechan{\i0}, when \Ndid you manage to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how to cook something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we had this when I went drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the other girls in \Nmy seminar the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so delicious that I \Nwanted everyone to have some,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I asked for the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'm surprised they gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, in any case, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.33,0:17:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this. Your father \Ncompletely mistook the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the reservation \Nwas for next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a comedy routine...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just about to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.87,0:17:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, paella?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuri-{\i1}oneechan{\i0} made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Kagami got all \Nthe ingredients for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even went all the way \Nto a distant supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we have some too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who took the mussels?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mussels?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, was I not supposed to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I was thinking \Nabout eating those last!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then write your name on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S'up. I'll take a detour with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have something you want to buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new book from Shin Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't have much time to read lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with all the assignments we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I have a pile of unread \Nmanga next to my pillow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always end up reaching \Nout for the newest ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda know how that feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read what you already have, \Ninstead of buying something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when you buy it first, \Nyou feel relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, you feel like you're \Nmissing something... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me to agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Star{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning Luckies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll deliver an energetic \Ninstallment again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.04,0:19:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time flies by... This week's {\i1}Lucky \NChannel {\i0}is already the 17th! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your navigator is-- all \Nred roses have thorns--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the platypus of the idol \Nindustry, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we have invited \Na very big-named guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to make me wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm showing on screen? \NI'm sorry, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, today's guest is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Special Guest - Mr. Meito Anizawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Anime Manager, Meito Anizawa! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This show has no tension whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.79,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, well, {\i1}Lucky Star {\i0}is an anime \Nshow that draws out the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of ordinary high schoolers in a \Nvery relaxed, peaceful atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this segment, {\i1}Lucky Channel{\i0}, is \Nalso rather relaxed, and has a low...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.77,0:20:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Do you know the \Nthree necessary elements
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the success of an anime show?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three elements? Let's see,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the voice actors, the animation \Nitself, and the script?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My uniform is burning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love, time, and budget that the \Nstaff and cast pour into the title!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's not a matter that \Nwe can do something about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Even if the \Noriginal work is wonderful,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's meaningless if you \Ndon't have a good script!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the voice actors are gung-ho,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if there is no color to the \Nanimation, it won't succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, line art is plenty for Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro-ishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone puts their lives on \Nthe line for their own part!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love and passion put towards a \Nwork, grinding your body to dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is what creates a wonderful series!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You're Miss Akira \NKogami right now, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now? I've always been \NAkira, past to present.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.30,0:21:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have overwhelming love \Nwhen you were playing Rou_an,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gaor_nger, P_tato, or Mai_ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have regrets for any of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.04,0:21:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn yourself out as Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I will burn out as Minoru Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well said, Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll start off with \Nhow to catch a crowd at an event!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the host for a big \Nevent the other day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the hard work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was given such an important role. \NI was nervous the entire time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not yet, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:01.29,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Shiraishi, take care \Nof the rest for me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, your ad-libs are weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lose against someone like Sugita!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:05.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Minoru Shiraishi Theater"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, missus! Are you dissatisfied \Nwith your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.76,0:22:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! This is Minoru Shiraishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's get on with the song now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Vague sunshine? Does that mean \NI'm at a disadvantage? Smooch! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The wrapping increases, hey, \Nis that a disadvantage? Wait! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.04,0:22:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Let's do it, you do it, that's \Ntime to catch 'n' release, yo! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I say, I say, funny funny, \Ndarlin' darlin' freeze! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.29,0:22:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Kinda lethargic, something's \Nkinda comin' out ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.50,0:22:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I love you... oh wait, one \Nof those was different ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Worrywarts, high metal bars, going... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ And that's enough! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.53,0:22:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The heated body of that \Nflying you-know-who ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's what you call a normal girl ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I'm the only one surprised? Seconds \Non ramen with wire-hard noodles! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Da da da da da ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.83,0:22:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not necessarily true.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Pom-poms cheer squad ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Electric Denina ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Careless, how is it? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Inheritance, how is it? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yeah! Feeling of existence, \Npanting Sozaira ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:23:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Haran haran furun furun horon \Nhoron hiren haren horonturo... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Take it away! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I should be the one that \Nwill be laughing in the end ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.29,0:23:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Because I have the sailor suit \N- > this is my conclusion ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ It's only Sunday! Already \Nin a bad mood? What to do? ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.20,0:23:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I really prefer the summer outfits \N← kya! Wah! Good! (cute!) < 3 ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yeah! Until we approach 3 \Npixels, no hesitations please ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Do your best, be energetic, \Nmy darlin', darlin' please! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:26.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what's with the next...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.36,0:23:26.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,That's boring, Shiraishi! {\an9}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with the cookie-cutter previews!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heil Blayking, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! But before that, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rule ♪1 in becoming a big-name voice actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rule ♪1!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't beat 'em, join 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How small-hearted!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.47,0:23:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: To Each Her Own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end for Mr. \NAnizawa, too. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger!
